  <h3>Highlights 2026</h3>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Easter Fires</strong> (April) – Traditional bonfires in Salzhemmendorf and Coppenbrügge</li>
    <li><strong>Ith-Hils Ultratrail</strong> (April) – 81 km trail running event</li>
    <li><strong>Coppenbrügge Spectaculum</strong> (August) – Medieval festival at the castle</li>
    <li><strong>7th Ith-Hils Hiking Day</strong> (September) – Free guided hikes</li>
    <li><strong>Rasti-Land Halloween</strong> (October) – Spooky theme park special</li>
    <li><strong>Christmas Markets</strong> (December) – Advent market and castle Christmas fair</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>Regular Events</h3>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Weekly Market</strong> – Every Wednesday 8am–1pm at the town hall, Salzhemmendorf</li>
